  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Amazing Weekend 2 - Search and Relax 2 Collector's Edition</strong> – Your Perfect Escape from Routine!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a world of inspiration and adventure with enhanced graphics and stunningly realistic locations. Go hiking, horseback riding, or sail across the waves – every minute of this game will give you the feeling of a real getaway!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191970/extras/f72ad8719d31a3a128cd933d6135c71b.poster.avif?t=1772653065\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191970/extras/f72ad8719d31a3a128cd933d6135c71b.webm?t=1772653065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191970/extras/f72ad8719d31a3a128cd933d6135c71b.mp4?t=1772653065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔍 <strong>What Awaits You:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>12 brand-new levels</strong> with engaging hidden object searches and mini-games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>8 additional mini-games</strong> for even more variety</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beautiful wallpapers</strong> to keep the adventure alive on your desktop</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Music player</strong> with relaxing melodies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Souvenir shop</strong> – collect unique items and build your own collections</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191970/extras/a93ddbb785911fb827436ebe0edf00d9.poster.avif?t=1772653065\" width=666 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191970/extras/a93ddbb785911fb827436ebe0edf00d9.webm?t=1772653065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191970/extras/a93ddbb785911fb827436ebe0edf00d9.mp4?t=1772653065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your observation skills, solve tricky puzzles, and enjoy every moment of this amazing journey!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ready for the perfect weekend?</strong> Your adventure begins right now!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Amazing Weekend 2 - Search and Relax 2 Collector's Edition</strong> – Your Perfect Escape from Routine!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a world of inspiration and adventure with enhanced graphics and stunningly realistic locations. Go hiking, horseback riding, or sail across the waves – every minute of this game will give you the feeling of a real getaway!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191970/extras/f72ad8719d31a3a128cd933d6135c71b.poster.avif?t=1772653065\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191970/extras/f72ad8719d31a3a128cd933d6135c71b.webm?t=1772653065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191970/extras/f72ad8719d31a3a128cd933d6135c71b.mp4?t=1772653065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔍 <strong>What Awaits You:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>12 brand-new levels</strong> with engaging hidden object searches and mini-games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>8 additional mini-games</strong> for even more variety</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beautiful wallpapers</strong> to keep the adventure alive on your desktop</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Music player</strong> with relaxing melodies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Souvenir shop</strong> – collect unique items and build your own collections</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191970/extras/a93ddbb785911fb827436ebe0edf00d9.poster.avif?t=1772653065\" width=666 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191970/extras/a93ddbb785911fb827436ebe0edf00d9.webm?t=1772653065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191970/extras/a93ddbb785911fb827436ebe0edf00d9.mp4?t=1772653065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your observation skills, solve tricky puzzles, and enjoy every moment of this amazing journey!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ready for the perfect weekend?</strong> Your adventure begins right now!</p>",
